# Local dev: copy to mobile/.env and override only when you want the iPhone to
# hit a non-LAN backend (e.g. Render staging). When unset, the app
# auto-derives the API host from Metro's hostUri (laptop's LAN IP at :3001).
#
# EXPO_PUBLIC_* names are bundled into the JS bundle at build time. Do not
# put secrets here — anything in this file ships to the device.

# Production / staging (Render):
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://layla-backend.onrender.com
